Resolution:  This is a fundamental problem with the mathematics.  Tl;dr - there
is a limit to how 'lopsided' the slices can be for this procedure to continue
working.  A proof will be forthcoming.  In the future, checks will need to be
built in that make sure the slices aren't too lopsided.
